## Implementation Status Self-Assessment

Use this checklist to honestly assess your ecosystem's current OMF implementation status:

| Requirement | Not Started | In Progress | Complete |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1. Dependency audit capability | ☐ | ☐ | ☐ |
| 2. Program governance authority | ☐ | ☐ | ☐ |
| 3. At least one active sustainment program | ☐ | ☐ | ☐ |
| 4. Transparent reporting mechanism | ☐ | ☐ | ☐ |
| 5. Portfolio review cadence | ☐ | ☐ | ☐ |

**Scoring:**
- 5/5 Complete: OMF compliant. Focus on program quality and portfolio expansion.
- 3–4/5 Complete: Partial implementation. Identify the missing requirements and prioritize them.
- 1–2/5 Complete: Early stage. Start with the dependency audit (Requirement 1) — everything else follows.
- 0/5 Complete: Not yet started. See [`README.md`](../README.md) Getting Started section.

